36
00:02:10,441 --> 00:02:13,662
increasing your bottom line, being an ally and advocate,

37
00:02:14,223 --> 00:02:16,584
avoiding lawsuits and bad publicity.

38
00:02:17,609 --> 00:02:20,570
Or like me, you've been unlucky in the lottery of birth

39
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:22,891
and would like to make things better for you

40
00:02:22,951 --> 00:02:24,691
and others who are also marginalized.

41
00:02:26,092 --> 00:02:27,392
My with them is this.

42
