45
00:02:36,295 --> 00:02:41,917
rich, tall, and white get all the opportunities

46
00:02:41,957 --> 00:02:44,978
in the world and those that are not are just unlucky.

47
00:02:46,594 --> 00:02:52,555
I grew up in the Philippines, born and raised in the Philippines, and at a young age I've

48
00:02:52,595 --> 00:02:54,316
seen the inequality of life.

49
