I moved to Singapore and was treated like a second class because of my color, which

50
00:03:00,917 --> 00:03:01,617
is brown.

51
00:03:03,618 --> 00:03:10,079
I moved to the U.S. and I'm an immigrant, and I experienced the microaggressions, but

52
00:03:10,119 --> 00:03:11,960
it was only here that I got woke.

53
00:03:15,926 --> 00:03:18,947
I could actually try to do something about the inequality

54
00:03:19,027 --> 00:03:21,308
and make things better for me and folks like me.

